## Definition of done

A change is complete only when all of these hold (edit to fit the project):

- Tests pass locally — run them and state the result.
- Lint/format clean.
- The **Verify** command was run and the observed behavior matches intent.
- `.ai_context/state.md` updated if project state changed; ADR appended to
  `.ai_context/decisions.md` if a design decision was made.

"Should work" is not done. Unverified work is reported as unverified.

## Project rules

